name: PowerGolf
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: power golf
des:
A very simple game of golf. The skill automatically generates a golf hole then you decide how much power to use (a number between 1 and 100) based on the distance to the hole, the club being used and the wind speed. Once you complete a hole the skill will tally up the strokes, give you a score. and then start a new hole.

Commands
Provide hitting power percentage (a number between 1 and 100 inclusive) : e.g. "fifty-eight"
Stop / Cancel : "Alexa stop", "Alexa cancel", "Alexa exit"
Get basic help : "Alexa help"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
